debug_attempts.error_analysis: ValueError: latex error converting to dvi. See log output above or the log file: media\Tex\30e4c5ae489b4574.log

The error was triggered by a LaTeX compilation issue when using the Tex mobject for displaying a matrix in LaTeX format. The original code used Tex with a raw string containing a LaTeX matrix environment, which led to conversion errors. In the fixed code, the matrix label is rendered with MathTex instead of Tex, which is more appropriate for mathematical typesetting.
